      "para_id": "Q004320.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Nanna-zišagĝal , chief butler , chief brewer , chief cup-bearer , overseer of the extispicy priests , is your servant ."
    }
